Tram han requirements:

-Adjust temperature using analog variable resistor.
-Display using 4x7segments LED. (required 12 output to control).
-Auto standby when iron rests on the case. (Lower temperature to 200Â°C). (required 1 input capture).
-Auto power off when resting for a long time (15 minutes). (required Timer interrupt).
